      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
         <p>The following material concerns businesses in which 
         <persname>N. F. Snarr</persname>had an interest, including the
         <corpname>Farmers Mutual Telephone System</corpname>and three
         general stores: 
         <corpname>Borden Brothers</corpname>; 
         <corpname>Snarr, Borden and Miley</corpname>and 
         <corpname>Snarr and Miley Company</corpname>. Many of the
         ledgers and account books were not labeled so the store to
         which they belong could not be determined.</p>
      </scopecontent>
